----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------About CPU--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Let us know what is the block diagram of computer:there will be a CPU let us imagine we are having input devices and output devices and there will be memory like primary memory and secondary memory
CPU:handles the process,input devices:mouse,keyboard,monitor
Primary memory:RAM,ROM  secondary memory:hard disk(gates)
RAM:(Random access memory)
->data and instructions are currently being processed are kept in primary memory
->it is volatile
->data is lost when system is truned off
ROM:(Read only memory)
->data and instructions are processed are kept in secondary memory
->it is non volatile
->data is not lost 
